    <item>
      <title>德拉吉称欧盟若不进行大规模支出和联合债务将面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/draghi-says-eu-in-danger-without-massive-spending-and-joint-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行前行长马里奥·德拉吉呼吁欧盟每年额外投资高达 8000 亿欧元（8840 亿美元），以增强欧盟竞争力，并承诺定期发行共同债券，与中国和美国竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/draghi-says-eu-in-danger-without-massive-spending-and-joint-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:02:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班暗示将缩小匈牙利央行行长候选人范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/orban-hints-at-narrowing-field-for-hungary-central-bank-governor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班表示，他计划合并财政部和经济部部长，并暗示受改革影响的一位部长将成为央行行长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/orban-hints-at-narrowing-field-for-hungary-central-bank-governor</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登寻求加强规则以降低心理健康护理成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/biden-seeks-stronger-rules-to-lower-mental-health-care-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫正在采取措施降低心理健康护理成本，力求确保美国人能够像享受身体健康福利一样享受心理健康和药物使用福利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/biden-seeks-stronger-rules-to-lower-mental-health-care-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
