    <item>
      <title>香港拒绝前往中国的德国活动人士入境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/hong-kong-refuses-entry-to-german-activist-who-went-to-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名德国政治活动家被拒绝从中国大陆进入香港，这是一个罕见的案例，这个曾经自由放任的金融中心的移民政策似乎比中国其他地区更为严格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/hong-kong-refuses-entry-to-german-activist-who-went-to-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 07:49:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本领导人高市在竞选中大肆宣扬支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/japan-s-takaichi-touts-spending-as-she-enters-leadership-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济安全保障大臣高市早苗承诺利用公共资金促进就业和增长，再次竞选日本首位女首相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/japan-s-takaichi-touts-spending-as-she-enters-leadership-race</guid>
